  "recipeInstructions": [
    {
      "@type": "HowToStep",
      "text": "In a medium bowl or mason jar, combine the 1/2 cup melted vegan butter, 1/2 cup hot sauce, 2 tsp vegan Worcestershire sauce, 2 tbsp white wine vinegar, 1/2 tsp white pepper, 1/4 tsp liquid smoke, and 1/4 tsp sea salt and whisk until completely combined."
